OL,3,CWhale song has its own 'phonetic
OL,4,Calphabet', research shows
OL,6,F"This marks a profound moment in
OL,7,Fadvancing our understanding of sperm
OL,8,Fwhales," Dr David Gruber, the founder
OL,9,Fof the long-term study, called Project
OL,10,FCETI, said. "It opens up the
OL,11,Fpossibility that sperm whales have an
OL,12,Fincredibly complex and nuanced
OL,13,Fcommunication system."
OL,15,FTo get enough examples of the sperm
OL,16,Fwhale clicks in Dominica, where there
OL,17,Fis a population of around 200 whales,
OL,18,Fscientists created a giant underwater
OL,19,Fstudio with microphones at different
OL,20,Fdepths.
